  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>Mystic Watcher</i>, you play as Lilliana, a witch who is forced to report the strange occurrences in her house—or else. Using the report system, you can click on objects that you suspect are anomalies, or use the camera report system to report any camera malfunctions or changes in the atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can inspect lights or search inside objects like cabinets and drawers to check for anomalies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367170/extras/09085b7f320388e3615bcdfb7c26b0a5.poster.avif?t=1755041191\" width=600 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367170/extras/09085b7f320388e3615bcdfb7c26b0a5.webm?t=1755041191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367170/extras/09085b7f320388e3615bcdfb7c26b0a5.mp4?t=1755041191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We've also provided you with a notebook that will store the anomalies you've reported!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367170/extras/848749ee91be4999dc96de55b178cd43.poster.avif?t=1755041191\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367170/extras/848749ee91be4999dc96de55b178cd43.webm?t=1755041191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367170/extras/848749ee91be4999dc96de55b178cd43.mp4?t=1755041191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We wish you good luck! ~</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>Mystic Watcher</i>, you play as Lilliana, a witch who is forced to report the strange occurrences in her house—or else. Using the report system, you can click on objects that you suspect are anomalies, or use the camera report system to report any camera malfunctions or changes in the atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can inspect lights or search inside objects like cabinets and drawers to check for anomalies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367170/extras/09085b7f320388e3615bcdfb7c26b0a5.poster.avif?t=1755041191\" width=600 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367170/extras/09085b7f320388e3615bcdfb7c26b0a5.webm?t=1755041191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367170/extras/09085b7f320388e3615bcdfb7c26b0a5.mp4?t=1755041191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We've also provided you with a notebook that will store the anomalies you've reported!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367170/extras/848749ee91be4999dc96de55b178cd43.poster.avif?t=1755041191\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367170/extras/848749ee91be4999dc96de55b178cd43.webm?t=1755041191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367170/extras/848749ee91be4999dc96de55b178cd43.mp4?t=1755041191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We wish you good luck! ~</p>",
